ems, while producing stellar masses at high-$z$ which are unphysically\nlarger than the estimated dynamical masses (particularly for\nlower-$\\sigma_{\\star}$ systems).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Sep 2014 20:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
