nd that the OGLE-IV Transient Detection System is\ncapable of detecting transients within the nuclei of galaxies. We present a few\ninteresting cases of nuclear transients of unknown type.\n  All data on the OGLE transients are made publicly available to the\nastronomical community via the OGLE website.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Sep 2014 14:10:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-04"}
